	"summary": "Moderate: curl security and bug fix update",
	"details": "The curl packages provide the libcurl library and the curl utility for downloading files from servers using various protocols, including HTTP, FTP, and LDAP.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* curl: FTP too eager connection reuse (CVE-2023-27535)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n\nBug Fix(es):\n\n* Cannot upload files to Jscape SFTP server: file gets created empty (BZ#2188029)",
